##
## A propos
##
@node about "About Calepin"

  Calepin is a little tool to keep address, telephone number, E-mail
etc.. of your friends. I saw many tools like this,but no one was the
one I was waiting for, so I decided to code one myself.
Calepin is not very powerful, it will only do its job and not more.

You will need OS 2.0 (I think)  and the MUI package installed to run
Calepin. Some word about  MUI: MUI is a library (a powerful library)
to draw GUI.This library is fantastic for the programmer and for the
users...so I use it ;-) See @{"mui" link mui}

Sorry for my (very) bad english,and the not really good explications
I hope you understand the documentation, and like the tool (?)

@endnode


